query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('mathoverflow')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('analytic-number-theory',
'ap.analysis-of-pdes',
'ca.classical-analysis-and-odes',
'cv.complex-variables',
'dg.differential-geometry',
'fa.functional-analysis',
'gn.general-topology',
'gt.geometric-topology',
'linear-algebra',
'nt.number-theory',
'reference-request')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name ilike '%stude%';
